des:
The popular Jivamukti Yoga method now also in your home - hands-free! practice with
Jivamukti Yoga Meditation and Yoga in short and long classes with international
renowned teachers such as Mitch and Olga Oskorbina.

Just say "Alexa, open Jivamukti Yoga" to start the skill and choose from meditation
or yoga classes when prompted. More classes below
https://digital.jivamuktiyoga.com

About Jivamukti Yoga: Jivamukti is a physical, ethical, and spiritual practice, combining a vigorous yoga as exercise, vinyasa-based physical style with adherence to five central tenets: shastra (scripture), bhakti (devotion), ahimsā (nonviolence, non-harming), nāda (music), and dhyana (meditation). It also emphasizes animal rights, veganism, environmentalism, and social activism.
